race.comment: POLKA DOT PINK (8) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing sixth (19.84) at this track last time. Should be very hard to beat this time. DANA CURLY (1) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at Wagga over 320m behind Mala Angel (19.07) in a Grade 5. Should be in this for a long way. BOGAN KNOWS (2) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 4th and beaten 7 lengths at Dubbo (18.82). Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Worth following up. MAVRO (7) placed last time and is worth some thought.
